dc_title_s: Africae nova descriptio; Auct: Guiljelmo Blaeuw.
dc_description_s: Note: Map highly colored. See Phillips, no. 455. Images of cities and peoples of Africa around map border. Has images of animals and sea creatures on map. 1 map: col.; 36 x 46 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
